WEBVTT

00:03.421 --> 00:05.256
- [ Manny ] Morning all
- Good morning, papi.

00:05.340 --> 00:07.634
Hump day.
Am I right, Jay?

00:07.717 --> 00:09.677
Your day ends at 2:30.

00:09.761 --> 00:12.430
Can't come fast enough.
Quittin' time. Am I right, Jay?

00:12.514 --> 00:15.266
Let's not
make this a thing.

00:15.350 --> 00:18.019
Whoa, whoa, whoa.
What is this?

00:18.102 --> 00:20.605
- Where's my soft-boiled egg?
- I scrambled it.

00:20.688 --> 00:22.273
It's good for you
to try new things.

00:22.357 --> 00:25.568
I don't want to try new things.
You can't just spring this on me.

00:25.652 --> 00:28.363
