This is not the biggest curveball...

00:28.446 --> 00:30.448
that life is going
to throw at you.

00:30.532 --> 00:32.534
Buddy, don't close yourself
off from new things.

00:32.616 --> 00:34.786
I ever tell you the story
about me and crab cakes?

00:34.911 --> 00:38.706
Thought I didn't like them.
Tried them. Love them. Wow.

00:38.790 --> 00:41.167
Are the movie rights
available for that one?

